casebody.head_matter:
In the Matter of DISCIPLINE OF James W. KENNEDY.
No. D-3001.
Supreme Court of the United States
Nov. 27, 2017.
James W. Kennedy, of Toms River, New Jersey, is suspended from the practice of law in this Court and a rule will issue, returnable within 40 days, requiring him to show cause why he should not be disbarred from the practice of law in this Court.
